{"comments":"Luminance - absolute light emission intensity.\n\nMeasured in candelas per square meter (cd/m², also called \"nits\"):\n- **0.0**: No light emission (black)\n- **80-200**: Typical SDR displays\n- **400-600**: Bright SDR displays\n- **1,000+**: HDR content (HDR10 standard)\n- **4,000+**: Peak HDR highlights\n- **10,000+**: Ultra HDR displays\n\n## vs Lightness\n\n- **Lightness (HSL)**: Perceptual - \"how light/dark does this look?\"\n- **Luminance**: Physical - \"how much light does this emit?\"\n\nLuminance is for:\n- Emissive UI elements (glowing buttons, neon text)\n- HDR rendering (bloom effects, bright highlights)\n- Light source definitions (how bright is this light?)\n- Self-illuminating materials\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- Glow effects (button with 200 nit glow)\n- HDR content (sunset at 4000 nits peak)\n- Light sources (LED panel at 500 nits)\n- Emissive materials (neon sign at 1000 nits)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[80,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[80,1]},"title":"eqLuminance"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[81,1]},"title":"ordLuminance"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[83,1]},"title":"showLuminance"}],"comments":"Luminance value in nits (cd/m²)\n\nRepresents absolute light emission intensity. 0 = no light, higher values\n= brighter emission. Unbounded to support HDR (can exceed 10,000 nits).\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[78,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[78,1]},"title":"Luminance"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a luminance value, clamping to >= 0.0\n\nNegative luminance is physically meaningless and is clamped to 0.\nUpper bound is unbounded to support HDR.\n\n```purescript\nluminance 0.0      -- No emission (black)\nluminance 100.0    -- Typical display\nluminance 1000.0   -- HDR content\nluminance (-50.0)  -- Clamped to 0.0\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[101,1]},"title":"luminance"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create luminance from integer nit value\n\nCommon in display specifications and UI:\n```purescript\nfromInt 100   -- 100 nits (typical display)\nfromInt 1000  -- 1000 nits (HDR)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[111,1]},"title":"fromInt"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a luminance value without clamping\n\nUse only when you know the value is valid (>= 0.0).\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[117,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[117,1]},"title":"unsafeLuminance"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract the raw Number value (nits)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[183,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[183,1]},"title":"unwrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Round to nearest integer nit\n\nUseful for display and serialization:\n```purescript\ntoInt (luminance 147.3)  -- 147\ntoInt (luminance 999.8)  -- 1000\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[193,26],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[193,1]},"title":"toInt"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to Number (alias for unwrap)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[197,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[197,1]},"title":"toNumber"},{"children":[],"comments":"Scale luminance by a factor\n\nUseful for relative adjustments:\n```purescript\nscale 2.0 (luminance 100.0)  -- Double brightness → 200 nits\nscale 0.5 (luminance 100.0)  -- Half brightness → 50 nits\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Luminance"],"Luminance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Luminance.purs","start":[131,1]},"title":"scale"},{"children":[],"comments":"Increase luminance by amount\n\n```purescript\nincrease 